Yemeni rebels?\"}, {'id': 53, 'start': 314.8399963378906, 'end': 319.82000732421875, 'text': ' Joining me to discuss these questions is retired Israeli Air Force Brigadier General Israel'}, {'id': 54, 'start': 319.82000732421875, 'end': 326.3599853515625, 'text': \" Relik Shafir, who was one of the pilots who took part in the bombing of Iraq's Osirak\"}, {'id': 55, 'start': 326.3599853515625, 'end': 328.7200012207031, 'text': ' nuclear reactor in 1981.'}, {'id': 56, 'start': 329.239990234375, 'end': 332.55999755859375, 'text': ' Relik, thank you for joining us on Security Brief.'}, {'id': 57, 'start': 332.55999755859375, 'end': 335.55999755859375, 'text': \" Let's start with the obvious big question.\"}, {'id': 58, 'start': 335.55999755859375, 'end': 342.55999755859375, 'text': \" Even if Israel wanted to go it alone in trying to take out Iran's nuclear program, does it\"}, {'id': 59, 'start': 342.55999755859375, 'end': 345.6400146484375, 'text': ' have the military capability to do so?'}, {'id': 60, 'start': 345.6400146484375, 'end': 349.79998779296875, 'text': ' Well, to a very limited extent.'}, {'id': 61, 'start': 349.79998779296875, 'end': 357.1400146484375, 'text': ' Just for an example, a B-2 bomber can carry the bunker buster, which weighs 25,000 pounds.'}, {'id': 62, 'start': 357.1400146484375, 'end': 360.0199890136719, 'text': \" That's this U.S.-manufactured bomb.\"}, {'id': 63, 'start': 360.0199890136719, 'end': 365.29998779296875, 'text': ' The heaviest weapon that an Israeli F-15 can take is about 3,000 pounds.'}, {'id': 64, 'start': 365.29998779296875, 'end': 366.5400085449219, 'text': \" That's a big gap.\"}, {'id': 65, 'start': 366.5400085449219, 'end': 376.94000244140625, 'text': \" It's a big gap, and it means that the ability to bomb and get into a very deep concrete\"}, {'id': 66, 'start': 376.94000244140625, 'end': 384.2200012207031, 'text': ' and stone encampment is limited.'}, {'id': 67, 'start': 384.2200012207031, 'end': 391.0199890136719, 'text': ' So I would say that we can take out some of their program, roll them back a little,'}, {'id': 68, 'start': 391.0199890136719, 'end': 394.05999755859375, 'text': ' but we cannot stop the program altogether.'}, {'id': 69, 'start': 394.05999755859375, 'end': 395.05999755859375, 'text': ' I see.'}, {'id': 70, 'start': 395.05999755859375, 'end': 398.9800109863281, 'text': ' What about, besides bombing, other potential alternatives?'}, {'id': 71, 'start': 398.9800109863281, 'end': 401.82000732421875, 'text': ' For example, covert operations.'}, {'id': 72, 'start': 401.82000732421875, 'end': 407.5400085449219, 'text': \" Just note that just in the past couple of weeks, we've seen some very mysterious explosions\"}, {'id': 73, 'start': 407.5400085449219, 'end': 408.5400085449219, 'text': ' in Iran.'}, {'id': 74, 'start': 408.5400085449219, 'end': 415.17999267578125, 'text': ' There was a Shaheed-Rajipur explosion, there was a factory in Mashhad, a power plant.'}, {'id': 75, 'start': 415.17999267578125, 'end': 422.2200012207031, 'text': ' How effective could covert operations, together with or by themselves, be in stopping or delaying'}, {'id': 76, 'start': 422.2200012207031, 'end': 423.3800048828125, 'text': ' the Iran nuclear program?'}, {'id': 77, 'start': 423.3800048828125, 'end': 426.70001220703125, 'text': \" Oh, it can delay, but it won't stop.\"}, {'id': 78, 'start': 426.70001220703125, 'end': 433.1400146484375, 'text': ' The program, the Iranian program, has been on from 1988, when Khomeini told his generals'}, {'id': 79, 'start': 433.1400146484375, 'end': 439.0199890136719, 'text': ' at the end of the war with the Iraqis, we need a weapon of leverage.'}, {'id': 80, 'start': 439.0199890136719, 'end': 445.05999755859375, 'text': \" That's when the program started, not seeing Israel as a target, but a fleet.\"}, {'id': 81, 'start': 445.05999755859375, 'end': 450.3399963378906, 'text': ' It has turned towards Israel, and that, in order to release the pressure off Saudi Arabia'}, {'id': 82, 'start': 450.3399963378906, 'end': 455.29998779296875, 'text': ' and Egypt, who have been at odds for four or five centuries at least.'}, {'id': 83, 'start': 455.29998779296875, 'end': 456.29998779296875, 'text': ' Right.'}, {'id': 84, 'start': 456.29998779296875, 'end': 461.4200134277344, 'text': ' Now, there have been some reports, Relic, that even as early as this month, Prime Minister'}, {'id': 85, 'start': 461.4200134277344, 'end': 468.0199890136719, 'text': ' Netanyahu was hoping for, or working towards, some kind of military operation or security'}, {'id': 86, 'start': 468.0199890136719, 'end': 473.05999755859375, 'text': ' operation against Iran nuclear reactors, and President Trump ordered a halt to that.'}, {'id': 87, 'start': 473.05999755859375, 'end': 475.5400085449219, 'text': ' He wants to see if diplomacy can work.'}, {'id': 88, 'start': 475.5400085449219, 'end': 481.260009765625, 'text': \" Obviously, it's a political, a diplomatic question about whether Israel could do that,\"}, {'id': 89, 'start': 481.260009765625, 'end': 484.6199951171875, 'text': ' go ahead without US approval, or even against the wishes of the US.'}, {'id': 90, 'start': 484.6199951171875, 'end': 491.1000061035156, 'text': ' But there is a security element as well, because the US and Israel are so, or certainly Israel'}, {'id': 91, 'start': 491.1000061035156, 'end': 494.3800048828125, 'text': \" is so dependent, or they're co-dependent in the region together.\"}, {'id': 92, 'start': 494.3800048828125, 'end': 500.5400085449219, 'text': ' So how wise would it be for Israel to move ahead without US approval, or even a scenario'}, {'id': 93, 'start': 500.5400085449219, 'end': 503.8599853515625, 'text': \" in which it perhaps doesn't even inform the US?\"}, {'id': 94, 'start': 503.8599853515625, 'end': 510.5799865722656, 'text': ' Well, that is very unlikely to happen because of the repercussions following that.'}, {'id': 95, 'start': 510.5799865722656, 'end': 515.5, 'text': ' And remember that Israel is probably the only ally that we have at this time in the Western'}, {'id': 96, 'start': 515.5, 'end': 517.8599853515625, 'text': ' world.'}, {'id': 97, 'start': 517.8599853515625, 'end': 528.8800048828125, 'text': \" The US has other things in its basket, such as the Ukrainian war, and let's not forget\"}, {'id': 98, 'start': 528.8800048828125, 'end': 530.97998046875, 'text': ' China and Taiwan.'}, {'id': 99, 'start': 530.97998046875, 'end': 538.1799926757812, 'text': ' Maybe the Chinese will see an attack by the US on Iran as a go-ahead for them to attack'}, {'id': 100, 'start': 538.1799926757812, 'end': 539.5, 'text': ' Taiwan.'}, {'id': 101, 'start': 539.5, 'end': 546.260009765625, 'text': ' So all these actually have to be taken into account when we think of a more global look'}, {'id': 102, 'start': 546.3800048828125, 'end': 549.3800048828125, 'text': ' at what is happening between ourselves and Iran.'}, {'id': 103, 'start': 549.3800048828125, 'end': 550.3800048828125, 'text': ' Right.'}, {'id': 104, 'start': 550.3800048828125, 'end': 557.8599853515625, 'text': ' Now, if the US should reach a deal with Iran that may fall short, for example, of dismantling'}, {'id': 105, 'start': 557.8599853515625, 'end': 563.1199951171875, 'text': ' its civilian nuclear program, at some point the security establishment presumably will'}, {'id': 106, 'start': 563.1199951171875, 'end': 569.4600219726562, 'text': ' be asked by the government if Israel can live with such a deal.'}, {'id': 107, 'start': 569.4600219726562, 'end': 572.8200073242188, 'text': ' What threat does that pose to the security of Israel?'}, {'id': 108, 'start': 572.8200073242188, 'end': 577.5399780273438, 'text': ' How would they likely answer that?'}, {'id': 109, 'start': 577.5399780273438, 'end': 585.8800048828125, 'text': \" The 2015 agreement was supported by a lot of people in Israel who said it's much better\"}, {'id': 110, 'start': 585.8800048828125, 'end': 590.8200073242188, 'text': ' to have a limited control as it was in the 2015.'}, {'id': 111, 'start': 590.8200073242188, 'end': 593.8200073242188, 'text': ' But also opposed by some security analysts.'}, {'id': 112, 'start': 593.8200073242188, 'end': 594.8200073242188, 'text': ' Very few.'}, {'id': 113, 'start': 594.8200073242188, 'end': 602.4199829101562, 'text': ' And Netanyahu insisted on going on and pushing for the annulment of that agreement, and as'}, {'id': 114, 'start': 602.4199829101562, 'end': 608.3400268554688, 'text': \" a result what we're seeing now is that Iran is ever closer to a nuclear weapon.\"}, {'id': 115, 'start': 608.3400268554688, 'end': 614.6599731445312, 'text': ' So getting them down to an enrichment of about three and a half percent, four percent for'}, {'id': 116, 'start': 614.6599731445312, 'end': 623.3800048828125, 'text': \" civilian use, it's very difficult to explain in the whole world why this can't be done,\"}, {'id': 117, 'start': 623.3800048828125, 'end': 630.4199829101562, 'text': ' being able to control all of the sites, including the military sites, by US inspectors.'}, {'id': 118, 'start': 630.4199829101562, 'end': 636.7000122070312, 'text': \" Well, of course, that's part of the key elements of the deal, inspection of those plants, whether\"}, {'id': 119, 'start': 636.7000122070312, 'end': 638.1400146484375, 'text': ' that be sufficient.'}, {'id': 120, 'start': 638.1400146484375, 'end': 642.219970703125, 'text': ' But another criticism of the 2015 deal is it did nothing to address, for example, the'}, {'id': 121, 'start': 642.219970703125, 'end': 644.9000244140625, 'text': ' ballistic missile program of Iran.'}, {'id': 122, 'start': 644.9000244140625, 'end': 650.260009765625, 'text': \" And we've seen, unfortunately in Israel, a direct result of that ballistic missile program\"}, {'id': 123, 'start': 650.260009765625, 'end': 656.260009765625, 'text': ' just this past week with the Houthi successful attack on Ben Gurion Airport.'}, {'id': 124, 'start': 656.260009765625, 'end': 661.02001953125, 'text': ' Could Israel live with no limitations at all, or what kind of security threat would'}, {'id': 125, 'start': 661.02001953125, 'end': 666.02001953125, 'text': \" it be if there would be a deal with no limitations, for example, on Iran's ballistic missile program\"}, {'id': 126, 'start': 666.02001953125, 'end': 671.7000122070312, 'text': ' or its support for delivering those ballistic missiles to terror groups like the Houthis?'}, {'id': 127, 'start': 671.7000122070312, 'end': 677.0599975585938, 'text': \" It's a good question that has to do with world politics.\"}, {'id': 128, 'start': 677.0599975585938, 'end': 681.3800048828125, 'text': \" What about North Korea's ballistic missiles?\"}, {'id': 129, 'start': 681.3800048828125, 'end': 685.3800048828125, 'text': \" I understand that, but I'm talking specifically about the security threat those missiles pose\"}, {'id': 130, 'start': 685.5, 'end': 686.5, 'text': ' to Israel.'}, {'id': 131, 'start': 686.5, 'end': 693.260009765625, 'text': ' Yes, but they could take North Korean missiles and use them, and it would be very difficult'}, {'id': 132, 'start': 693.260009765625, 'end': 700.739990234375, 'text': ' to push this through the Europeans, who will most likely not support this part of the deal,'}, {'id': 133, 'start': 700.739990234375, 'end': 701.739990234375, 'text': ' unfortunately.'}, {'id': 134, 'start': 701.739990234375, 'end': 702.739990234375, 'text': ' Right.'}, {'id': 135, 'start': 702.739990234375, 'end': 707.8200073242188, 'text': \" Well, let's talk a little about that Houthi attack on Ben Gurion Airport.\"}, {'id': 136, 'start': 707.8200073242188, 'end': 713.4199829101562, 'text': ' As someone who certainly knows about air defense systems, how is it possible that that one'}, {'id': 137, 'start': 713.4199829101562, 'end': 719.02001953125, 'text': \" missile managed to evade both the Israel's Ahrar program, which has shown great success\"}, {'id': 138, 'start': 719.02001953125, 'end': 725.1400146484375, 'text': ' in other circumstances, including attacks directly from Iran, and the U.S. THAAD missile'}, {'id': 139, 'start': 725.1400146484375, 'end': 730.1799926757812, 'text': ' system, which many people thought was the really most advanced air defense system that'}, {'id': 140, 'start': 730.1799926757812, 'end': 731.3800048828125, 'text': ' has been created?'}, {'id': 141, 'start': 731.3800048828125, 'end': 735.02001953125, 'text': ' Well, you could argue which one is the most advanced.'}, {'id': 142, 'start': 735.02001953125, 'end': 739.3800048828125, 'text': ' Well, neither performed to distinction this past week.'}, {'id': 143, 'start': 739.3800048828125, 'end': 745.739990234375, 'text': \" That basically, we're talking about a 95% probability of direct hit.\"}, {'id': 144, 'start': 745.739990234375, 'end': 751.4600219726562, 'text': \" We're talking about a closure speed of about two miles per second.\"}, {'id': 145, 'start': 751.4600219726562, 'end': 761.3800048828125, 'text': ' And a small miss, or a small change in direction of the target, can cause a miss.'}, {'id': 146, 'start': 761.3800048828125, 'end': 767.6599731445312, 'text': ' Maybe we need three missiles per, to shoot three missiles per Houthi missile to make'}, {'id': 147, 'start': 767.6599731445312, 'end': 770.6400146484375, 'text': \" sure that we're closer to 100.\"}, {'id': 148, 'start': 770.6400146484375, 'end': 777.3400268554688, 'text': ' But there is no hermetic answer to these, and we will have to suffer the consequences'}, {'id': 149, 'start': 777.3400268554688, 'end': 780.9400024414062, 'text': ' every now and then if it goes on for a long time.'}, {'id': 150, 'start': 780.9400024414062, 'end': 786.9400024414062, 'text': ' Which does raise the question, though, you talk about adding on, does Israel, is its'}, {'id': 151, 'start': 786.9400024414062, 'end': 793.5, 'text': \" air defense shield sufficient, given the fact that it's now being attacked in multiple directions?\"}, {'id': 152, 'start': 793.5, 'end': 798.5, 'text': \" By the Houthis, certainly we've seen direct fire from Iran, always a threat of Hezbollah,\"}, {'id': 153, 'start': 798.5, 'end': 804.3800048828125, 'text': ' and of course, even these militias in Iraq who are allied with Iran.'}, {'id': 154, 'start': 804.3800048828125, 'end': 814.3800048828125, 'text': \" I think we've seen, from April into October of 2024, the ability to stop most of the missiles\"}, {'id': 155, 'start': 814.3800048828125, 'end': 815.3800048828125, 'text': ' coming in.'}, {'id': 156, 'start': 815.3800048828125, 'end': 817.8200073242188, 'text': ' Some will come in and create some damage.'}, {'id': 157, 'start': 817.8200073242188, 'end': 828.8200073242188, 'text': ' But just to let you know, one of those missiles, an F-15 fully loaded, has 24 of those missiles'}, {'id': 158, 'start': 828.8200073242188, 'end': 832.0599975585938, 'text': ' stacked up when it goes to bombing.'}, {'id': 159, 'start': 832.0599975585938, 'end': 836.4199829101562, 'text': ' So just to understand the damage that could be caused.'}, {'id': 160, 'start': 836.4199829101562, 'end': 837.4199829101562, 'text': ' Right.'}, {'id': 161, 'start': 837.4199829101562, 'end': 842.9000244140625, 'text': \" I do want to just reference the operation that's been announced in the Gaza Strip, in\"}, {'id': 162, 'start': 842.9000244140625, 'end': 850.219970703125, 'text': ' the context of Israel fighting a multi-front war, and potentially even contemplating a'}, {'id': 163, 'start': 850.219970703125, 'end': 855.7000122070312, 'text': ' strike on Iran, which would really extend that front.'}, {'id': 164, 'start': 855.7000122070312, 'end': 861.3800048828125, 'text': ' We could see the north really heat up again, direct attacks.'}, {'id': 165, 'start': 861.3800048828125, 'end': 866.7000122070312, 'text': ' Given the scope of the operation planned in Gaza, is the IEDF, does it have the capability'}, {'id': 166, 'start': 866.7000122070312, 'end': 871.780029296875, 'text': ' to contend with all of these challenges, all potentially at the same time?'}, {'id': 167, 'start': 871.780029296875, 'end': 878.5800170898438, 'text': \" In Lebanon, in Syria and Iran, and the Houthis, it's all Air Force, and it doesn't take the\"}, {'id': 168, 'start': 878.5800170898438, 'end': 884.3400268554688, 'text': ' whole Air Force to take care of those scenarios.'}, {'id': 169, 'start': 884.3400268554688, 'end': 893.8599853515625, 'text': ' In Gaza itself, the Air Force, mainly using RPVs, or UAVs, with the forces to make sure'}, {'id': 170, 'start': 893.8599853515625, 'end': 898.3800048828125, 'text': \" that they're defended as they move along, is the main force.\"}, {'id': 171, 'start': 898.3800048828125, 'end': 904.0599975585938, 'text': ' Because the Israeli Air Force does not want to use a one-ton bomb in order to take out'}, {'id': 172, 'start': 904.0599975585938, 'end': 911.02001953125, 'text': ' small munition depots or terrorists, in order not to create collateral damage.'}, {'id': 173, 'start': 911.02001953125, 'end': 915.6599731445312, 'text': ' So the Air Force can do all of these missions.'}, {'id': 174, 'start': 915.6599731445312, 'end': 917.9000244140625, 'text': \" It's strong enough and big enough.\"}, {'id': 175, 'start': 917.9000244140625, 'end': 925.5, 'text': ' The ground forces, they will move in probably after Trump leaves, at a certain manner that'}, {'id': 176, 'start': 925.5, 'end': 927.9400024414062, 'text': \" we don't really know yet how.\"}, {'id': 177, 'start': 927.9400024414062, 'end': 928.9400024414062, 'text': ' Understood.'}, {'id': 178, 'start': 928.9400024414062, 'end': 931.6199951171875, 'text': ' And again, just one last point on this.'}, {'id': 179, 'start': 931.6199951171875, 'end': 937.5399780273438, 'text': \" Gaza, Israel's military operation in Gaza, so far as you know, does have the U.S. support,\"}, {'id': 180, 'start': 937.5399780273438, 'end': 941.5800170898438, 'text': ' which is crucial, especially when it comes to some of the issues involved, for example,'}, {'id': 181, 'start': 941.5800170898438, 'end': 944.8599853515625, 'text': ' replacing the humanitarian aid system.'}, {'id': 182, 'start': 944.8599853515625, 'end': 950.780029296875, 'text': \" Does that, in a sense, perhaps limit Israel's options in dealing, perhaps, with Iran, with\"}, {'id': 183, 'start': 950.780029296875, 'end': 956.4199829101562, 'text': \" the Houthis, where the U.S. has told Israel, we're going to handle it, because of the interdependence\"}, {'id': 184, 'start': 956.4199829101562, 'end': 963.1400146484375, 'text': ' now of Israel on the U.S. for that kind of military operation, for example, in Gaza?'}, {'id': 185, 'start': 963.1400146484375, 'end': 968.0999755859375, 'text': ' Well, obviously, the political support of the U.S. is of utmost importance.'}, {'id': 186, 'start': 968.0999755859375, 'end': 975.9199829101562, 'text': \" And I don't see Israel acting against Trump's will, else we will see how he deals with his\"}, {'id': 187, 'start': 975.9199829101562, 'end': 980.02001953125, 'text': ' own staff when they misbehave, so to speak.'}, {'id': 188, 'start': 980.02001953125, 'end': 985.219970703125, 'text': \" And so Israel doesn't want to go against Trump, because then it will really be alone.\"}, {'id': 189, 'start': 985.219970703125, 'end': 991.0599975585938, 'text': \" And this is something that we probably won't want to do at this time, under any duress.\"}, {'id': 190, 'start': 991.0599975585938, 'end': 992.0599975585938, 'text': ' All right.'}, {'id': 191, 'start': 992.0599975585938, 'end': 997.0599975585938, 'text': \" So right now, the game is, the ball is in, it would seem, in Washington's court, and\"}, {'id': 192, 'start': 997.0599975585938, 'end': 1002.6199951171875, 'text': \" with U.S. President Trump, and these negotiations, and maybe we'll be seeing some answers during\"}, {'id': 193, 'start': 1002.6199951171875, 'end': 1007.780029296875, 'text': ' his visit, his planned visit to the region next week.'}, {'id': 194, 'start': 1007.780029296875, 'end': 1015.02001953125, 'text': \" Syria is home to over 600,000 Druze, a little over 3% of that nation's total population,\"}, {'id': 195, 'start': 1015.02001953125, 'end': 1018.219970703125, 'text': ' and more than half of all the Druze worldwide.'}, {'id': 196, 'start': 1018.219970703125, 'end': 1023.739990234375, 'text': \" Now most live in the country's southwest corner, an area bordering Golan and the Golan Heights\"}, {'id': 197, 'start': 1023.739990234375, 'end': 1024.739990234375, 'text': ' in Israel.'}, {'id': 198, 'start': 1024.739990234375, 'end': 1028.780029296875, 'text': ' In recent weeks, more than 100 people have been killed in violence between the Syrian'}, {'id': 199, 'start': 1028.780029296875, 'end': 1032.5, 'text': ' Druze and pro-government Islamist forces.'}, {'id': 200, 'start': 1032.5, 'end': 1037.219970703125, 'text': ' The Syrian Druze have maintained close ties through the years with their fellow Druze'}, {'id': 201, 'start': 1037.219970703125, 'end': 1043.5799560546875, 'text': ' in Israel, and in their hour of need, they are calling on Jerusalem for help.'}, {'id': 202, 'start': 1043.5799560546875, 'end': 1044.9000244140625, 'text': ' And Israel is responding.'}, {'id': 203, 'start': 1044.9000244140625, 'end': 1050.260009765625, 'text': ' The Israeli Air Force struck several military targets in and around Damascus over the weekend,'}, {'id': 204, 'start': 1050.260009765625, 'end': 1055.4200439453125, 'text': ' in what the government called, quote, a clear message to the Syrian regime to not allow'}, {'id': 205, 'start': 1055.4200439453125, 'end': 1061.4599609375, 'text': ' the deployment of forces south of Damascus, or pose any threat to the Druze community.'}, {'id': 206, 'start': 1061.4599609375, 'end': 1067.6600341796875, 'text': \" IDF forces also deployed in several Druze villages that sit along Syria's border area\"}, {'id': 207, 'start': 1067.6600341796875, 'end': 1071.3399658203125, 'text': ' with northern Israel, providing aid and security.'}, {'id': 208, 'start': 1071.3399658203125, 'end': 1077.219970703125, 'text': ' And some two dozen Druze civilians have been evacuated by the IDF from Syria to the Ziv'}, {'id': 209, 'start': 1077.219970703125, 'end': 1079.699951171875, 'text': ' Hospital in Sfat for medical treatment.'}, {'id': 210, 'start': 1131.3399658203125, 'end': 1152.780029296875, 'text': \" Still with us is Israel's Relic Shafir.\"}, {'id': 211, 'start': 1152.780029296875, 'end': 1159.219970703125, 'text': \" And Relic, let me ask you, how far can Israel go given, as we've discussed, the stretching\"}, {'id': 212, 'start': 1159.219970703125, 'end': 1162.5799560546875, 'text': ' of its forces at this time to provide protection for the Syrian Druze?'}, {'id': 213, 'start': 1162.5799560546875, 'end': 1168.02001953125, 'text': ' Well, most of the protection would be done by the Air Force, UAVs, or fighter aircraft'}, {'id': 214, 'start': 1168.02001953125, 'end': 1175.9000244140625, 'text': ' if needed, to stop any attacking forces from getting close to Sueda, which is the major'}, {'id': 215, 'start': 1175.9000244140625, 'end': 1179.5400390625, 'text': ' Druze city.'}, {'id': 216, 'start': 1179.5799560546875, 'end': 1196.0999755859375, 'text': ' the Syrian regime that should they give their hand to attack the Druze, they will suffer'}, {'id': 217, 'start': 1196.0999755859375, 'end': 1198.93994140625, 'text': ' close to Damascus.'}, {'id': 218, 'start': 1198.93994140625, 'end': 1200.93994140625, 'text': \" And we'll see how that will go.\"}, {'id': 219, 'start': 1200.93994140625, 'end': 1208.93994140625, 'text': \" Otherwise, a lot of aid and make sure there's an open route to Jordan, which is also acting\"}, {'id': 220, 'start': 1208.93994140625, 'end': 1212.93994140625, 'text': ' against the Islamic Brotherhood, has been doing so lately.'}, {'id': 221, 'start': 1212.93994140625, 'end': 1213.93994140625, 'text': ' In Syria.'}, {'id': 222, 'start': 1213.93994140625, 'end': 1214.93994140625, 'text': ' Yes.'}, {'id': 223, 'start': 1214.93994140625, 'end': 1215.93994140625, 'text': ' No, in Jordan itself.'}, {'id': 224, 'start': 1215.93994140625, 'end': 1216.93994140625, 'text': ' In Jordan itself.'}, {'id': 225, 'start': 1216.93994140625, 'end': 1223.800048828125, 'text': \" So it's a concentration of forces to help the Druze, and this is also a sign for the\"}, {'id': 226, 'start': 1223.800048828125, 'end': 1229.8599853515625, 'text': ' Turks, who are pretty active in the northern part of Syria, not to go further south and'}, {'id': 227, 'start': 1229.8599853515625, 'end': 1233.4200439453125, 'text': ' actually de-conflict with Israel in that area.'}, {'id': 228, 'start': 1233.4200439453125, 'end': 1241.02001953125, 'text': ' Syria has gone back to the pre-1919 Sykes-Picot agreement that actually took all these tribes'}, {'id': 229, 'start': 1241.02001953125, 'end': 1243.0999755859375, 'text': ' and drew a line in the sand to make that Syria.'}, {'id': 230, 'start': 1243.0999755859375, 'end': 1244.0999755859375, 'text': ' Right.'}, {'id': 231, 'start': 1244.0999755859375, 'end': 1247.8199462890625, 'text': \" It's less a country than now a conglomeration of differing entities.\"}, {'id': 232, 'start': 1247.8199462890625, 'end': 1250.260009765625, 'text': ' I would say tribes and entities, yes.'}, {'id': 233, 'start': 1250.260009765625, 'end': 1251.260009765625, 'text': ' All right.'}, {'id': 234, 'start': 1251.260009765625, 'end': 1257.780029296875, 'text': \" Well, let's wish the best for the Druze there in Syria, who have been calling on Israel\"}, {'id': 235, 'start': 1257.780029296875, 'end': 1258.780029296875, 'text': ' for help.'}, {'id': 236, 'start': 1258.780029296875, 'end': 1263.5400390625, 'text': ' And, of course, Israel owes a debt to the Israeli Druze, who have been so a key part'}, {'id': 237, 'start': 1263.5400390625, 'end': 1267.5799560546875, 'text': ' of the Israeli military effort until this very day.'}, {'id': 238, 'start': 1267.5799560546875, 'end': 1272.6199951171875, 'text': ' Israel Relic, Shafir, thank you for joining us on an ILTV Security Brief.'}, {'id': 239, 'start': 1272.6199951171875, 'end': 1274.3399658203125, 'text': ' Thank you for having me.'}, {'id': 240, 'start': 1274.3399658203125, 'end': 1276.260009765625, 'text': ' And now a final word.'}, {'id': 241, 'start': 1276.260009765625, 'end': 1282.06005859375, 'text': ' Last week, Israel observed its Memorial Day, honoring the over 25,000 men and women who'}, {'id': 242, 'start': 1282.06005859375, 'end': 1287.219970703125, 'text': ' have fallen in defense of Israel and the Jewish national home over the years.'}, {'id': 243, 'start': 1287.219970703125, 'end': 1292.260009765625, 'text': ' Among the many ceremonies held that day was a very special one in Jerusalem, held in memory'}, {'id': 244, 'start': 1292.260009765625, 'end': 1297.260009765625, 'text': \" of some 50 members of Israel's ultra-Orthodox or Haredi community.\"}, {'id': 245, 'start': 1297.260009765625, 'end': 1303.6400146484375, 'text': ' Some 3,000 attendees took part in a memorial organized by the NGO Netzach Yehuda, named'}, {'id': 246, 'start': 1303.6400146484375, 'end': 1310.02001953125, 'text': ' after the battalion created by the IDF to especially enable Haredi soldiers to serve'}, {'id': 247, 'start': 1310.02001953125, 'end': 1314.739990234375, 'text': ' in combat roles without compromising their religious values.'}, {'id': 248, 'start': 1314.780029296875, 'end': 1321.9000244140625, 'text': ' The same week, some 400 Haredi men were enlisted in the IDF, but that is just a small percentage'}, {'id': 249, 'start': 1321.9000244140625, 'end': 1325.9000244140625, 'text': ' of the 10,000 draft notices sent out last year.'}, {'id': 250, 'start': 1325.9000244140625, 'end': 1332.06005859375, 'text': ' And some of those who did enlist found themselves harassed by Haredi anti-draft protesters as'}, {'id': 251, 'start': 1332.06005859375, 'end': 1335.8599853515625, 'text': ' they made their way to and from recruitment centers.'}, {'id': 252, 'start': 1335.8599853515625, 'end': 1340.780029296875, 'text': ' Now the issue of draft exemptions for the Haredi community is a complex one, and there'}, {'id': 253, 'start': 1340.780029296875, 'end': 1346.5799560546875, 'text': ' are legitimate disagreements over the best way to integrate the ultra-Orthodox into military'}, {'id': 254, 'start': 1346.5799560546875, 'end': 1350.699951171875, 'text': ' or national service, or even to do so.'}, {'id': 255, 'start': 1350.699951171875, 'end': 1355.219970703125, 'text': ' But speaking for myself, as an IDF veteran and the father of IDF veterans, there can'}, {'id': 256, 'start': 1355.219970703125, 'end': 1359.699951171875, 'text': ' be no excuse for the abuse of those Haredi youngsters that are prepared to share the'}, {'id': 257, 'start': 1359.699951171875, 'end': 1365.780029296875, 'text': ' burden of military duty with their Jewish brethren, or the silence of many Haredi political'}, {'id': 258, 'start': 1365.780029296875, 'end': 1369.780029296875, 'text': ' and rabbinical leaders to condemn this outrageous behavior.'}, {'id': 259, 'start': 1369.780029296875, 'end': 1375.0400390625, 'text': ' This is especially so as the IDF is now dealing with a serious manpower shortage as it fights'}, {'id': 260, 'start': 1375.0400390625, 'end': 1382.97998046875, 'text': ' a multi-front war, and many Israelis are contending with the crushing burden of months of reserve duty.'}, {'id': 261, 'start': 1382.97998046875, 'end': 1387.1800537109375, 'text': ' Shall your brothers go to war while you just sit here?'}, {'id': 262, 'start': 1387.1800537109375, 'end': 1393.739990234375, 'text': \" That's the question Moshe, Moses, asked the tribes of Gad and Reuben, as recorded in Bami\"}, {'id': 263, 'start': 1393.739990234375, 'end': 1395.6199951171875, 'text': \" Bar, the Bible's book of numbers.\"}, {'id': 264, 'start': 1395.97998046875, 'end': 1400.300048828125, 'text': ' It is a question no less relevant in the Israel of today.'}, {'id': 265, 'start': 1400.300048828125, 'end': 1404.06005859375, 'text': \" Thank you for joining us on ITL TV's Security Brief.\"}]}"